This project implements a real-time face recognitionâ€“based attendance system using Python, OpenCV, and the face_recognition library.
It automatically detects faces from a webcam, recognizes known individuals, and records their attendance in a CSV file with date and time.

ğŸš€ Features

Real-time face detection using webcam

Face recognition using pre-stored images

Automatic attendance marking

Attendance saved in date-wise CSV file

Each person is marked only once per session

Displays bounding box and name on detected face

